Naming convensions in java

-> every class in java should starts with upper case letter. If there are more than
   ome word in class name, then each class name should be in uppercase letter
   Ex: Employee, InputSream, FileInputStream, NosuchDataFoundException

-> every method,variables and objects shold starts with lowercase letter. Incase  there are more than one word defined, then first letter of each second word should  be in upper case letter
ex: display(), processData(), markStudentAttendence(), average, employee .. etc

-> all keywords and package names in java must be in lower case letters
   ex: int, if, class
-> all cont in java should be in upper case letters
   PI, MAX_AGE .. etc

   

